2.2 The immediate objectives of the project are:
1.	To provide opportunity for the local Liberian populace to actively participate in harnessing the TRC recommendations in relation to the four policy issues of Reconciliation, Amnesty, Reparation, Prosecution;
2.	To facilitate a forum for victims and perpetrators to mediate in the three regions;
3.	To provide a forum for dialogue among Liberians and partners on the TRC's findings and recommendations;
4.	To chart a course for national reconciliation.
